high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter to the left of the stove
Grab the knife off of the counter
Turn right and go to the counter to the right of the stove
Cut the loaf of bread on the counter into slices
Put the knife on the counter
Pick up one of the slices of bread
Turn left and go to the fridge
Put the bread in the fridge and then close the door. Then take the bread out
Turn around and go to the sink
Put the bread in the sink

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the stove.
Pick up a knife on the counter.
Turn and go to the bread on the counter.
Cut the bread on the counter.
Put the knife on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Turn and go to the refrigerator.
Chill the slice of bread in the refrigerator.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Put the slice of bread in the microwave.

high_descs: turn to the left and move to the counter that is to the left of the stove
pick up the sharp knife with the yellow handle that is to the left of the glass
turn to the right and move forward to the counter that is to the right of the stove
turn to face the counter in front of the loaf of bread and slice the loaf with the knife
stick the knife, straight up and down, in to the loaf of bread
pick up the end piece of the sliced loaf of bread
turn to the left and move forward to the fridge on the right, turn right to face the fridge
open the door of the refrigerator, put the slice of bread on the top shelf to the left of the tomato, close the door for eight seconds, open the door, remove the slice and close the door
turn to the right and move forward until the sink is on the right, turn to the right and move to the sink
open the door of the microwave that is above the sink, put the slice of bread into the microwave and close the door
anns.task_desc: put a slice of chilled bread in to the microwave
